description._content: Viewed larger, you see a bit inside various offices of these serious San Francisco towers. The left tower is One Maritime Plaza, and on the right are cascading Embarcadero Center towers 2, 3, and 4. Close in, 'FRANCISCO' reads in reverse against the dawn, visually beneath the Bay Bridge while actually that reads "Port of San Francisco" on the further foreground and not visible Ferry Building
